I"P<p>Cavaliers belonging to the order of the dragon dedicate themselves to a group of like-minded individuals, be it a mercenary company or a small band of adventurers. These cavaliers believe in loyalty and friendship, and are willing to lay down their lives to protect their allies.</p>

<h3 id="edicts">Edicts</h3>
<p>Cavaliers of the Dragon share the following edicts.</p>
<ul>
  <li>The cavalier must remain loyal to his allies and must always work to further the aims of the group.</li>
  <li>He must protect his allies from harm and defend their honor when called into doubt.</li>
</ul>
